{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1694-01_208","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Response touchant l’embarras où se trouve une Dame, à l’égard de son Amant","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", janvier 1694 [tome 1], p. 208-214.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Je vous ay marqué dans ma Lettre du mois de May dernier, l’embarras où se trouvoit une fort aimable &amp; spirituelle personne, qui aimant un Cavalier absolument pour luy-mesme, &amp; luy voyant prendre de l’attachement préjudiciable à celuy qu’il avoit fait paroistre long-temps pour elle, ne sçavoit si elle devoit l’en détourner, ou l’abandonner à son panchant, puis qu’il luy faisoit plaisir. Elle a demandé conseil, &amp; voicy ce qu’a pensé là-dessus M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" de la Ferrerie.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"RESPONSE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"Touchant l’embarras où se trouve une Dame, à l’égard de son Amant.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pouvez-vous avec tout l’esprit","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que vous avez, à ce qu’on dit,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Paroistre tant embarassêe ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tircis est insensible, helas !","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chassez-le de vostre pensée,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous n’aurez plus d’embarras.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais puis-je bannir de mon cœur","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cet aimable &amp; charmant vainqueur,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que j’aime d’une amour si pure ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus l’amour a de pureté,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus il est sensible à l’injure","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui vient de l’infidelité.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il est vray, mais innocemment,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je suis cause du changement","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont je me plains, &amp; qui m’offense.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Faites sur vous un noble effort,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Portez ce mal en patience,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il faut souffrir quand on a tort.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Peut-estre est-ce pour se vanger,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il feint ailleurs de s’engager,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans le fond, qu’il est fidelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourquoy donc vous tant chagriner ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Delicate, spirituelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez dû le deviner.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ouy, mais si veritablement,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tircis que j’aime tendrement,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Estoit inconstant &amp; volage.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Hé bien, changez à vostre tour.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On dit que vous estes si sage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand on est sage, adieu l’amour,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Helas ! ce conseil est bien dur,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon engagement est si pur,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et j’ay l’ame ferme &amp; constante.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aimez, souffrez, perseverez,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est-là d’une parfaite Amante","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le merite où vous aspirez.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais n’oserois-je faire voir,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans faire tort à mon devoir,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Combien ce changement me blesse ?","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si vous aimiez grossierement,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans égard, sans delicatesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous le pourriez fort librement.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Helas ! je sens que mon amour,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mille fois plus pur que le jour,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne peut souffrir nulle foiblesse.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Suspendez donc vostre douleur,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que toute vostre tendresse","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’éclate que dans vostre cœur.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Malgré son infidelité,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay tant de generosité,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je le cede à ma Rivale.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est là beaucoup vous avancer,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vostre tendresse est sans égale,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et rien ne peut la surpasser.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Non, je n’ay point d’autre desir,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de donner à son plaisir","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce qui peut le satisfaire.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce sentiment est genereux,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous ne pouvez jamais rien faire","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui vous soit plus avantageux.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je ne verray donc plus Tircis,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tranquille avec son Iris,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il triomphera de ma flame ?","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est à quoy je veux vous porter,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais consultez encor vostre ame","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avant que de l’executer.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Non, non. Je ne me flate point","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je puis en venir à ce point,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans qu’aucun retour me démente.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’il est ainsi, consolez-vous,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy content, vous serez contente","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus que s’il estoit vostre Epoux.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" C’est donc là vostre sentiment,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je dois suivre aveuglement,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si je veux conserver ma gloire ;","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’il en coûte à vostre vertu,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous n’aurez jamais la victoire","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’aprés avoir bien combattu.","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}}]}}}